node.text:
Thank you everyone, for helping me reach 200k on here! I appreciate all of you, even the bots! 
I think this is a good point in the story for me to take a brief hiatus! I’ll be using this time to finally rest, catch up on other work, and prepare the next part of the comic! I’m really excited to show you what I have planned... 

There will be a follow up to this comic on my Patreon this weekend for Patrons only! 
#comics #webcomics #comicart #comicartist #emmytherobot
